ic effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/190328/', '', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', 1767369485);
